msgstr "Ignorer toute configuration automatique des routes et les gérer manuellement"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/services/mqvpn.js
msgid "DNS servers"
msgstr "Serveurs DNS"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/services/mqvpn.js
